      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOVA'S FERN (6) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 5.5 lengths away in second (34.84) at Angle Park in a Grade 5/6 over 595m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Well placed and gets her chance. ADHANA MADI (8) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led for much of the way before being grabbed late, finishing a nose second at this track over 530m in 30.12. Has a strong record from box 8, including two wins. Expecting another good run. NITRO NEO (1) turned in a plain effort last time when sixth at Angle Park over 595m behind Big Diesel (35.73) in a Grade 5/6. Was in the money the start prior. Must be included in calculations. ZENVO YOYO (2) looks an each-way chance.",
